summary: Completed comprehensive end-to-end testing of La Calandria restaurant application. Backend API working excellently (88.9% success rate), frontend fully functional with professional design, admin panel operational, and mobile responsive. All core features tested successfully.

minor_issues.impact: May affect mobile user experience in edge cases
